"""
        Test that the inequality operator returns True when comparing two
        Credential structs with different credential values.
        """
a = objects.Credential(credential_value=objects.UsernamePasswordCredential(
    username='Fred', password='password1'))
b = objects.Credential(credential_value=objects.DeviceCredential(
    device_serial_number='serNum123456', password='secret',
    device_identifier='devID2233', network_identifier='netID9000',
    machine_identifier='machineID1', media_identifier='mediaID313'))
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
